				<h2><a href="/Sql-Injection-explained">SQL Injection Explained</a></h2>
				<p class="description">
				<span><p>SQL injection vulnerability allows attacker to pass ‚Äúinjection‚Äù of a SQL statment via the input data throught the web application. A successful SQL injection attack can read, modify or delete (Insert/Update/Delete) sensitive data from the database, execute administration operations on the database (such as shutdown the DBMS) or in some cases issue commands to the operating system.</p>
</span>
				</p>
