				<h2><a href="/Introduction-to-offensive-security-(Ethical-Hacking)">Introduction to Offensive Security (Ethical Hacking)</a></h2>
				<p class="description">
				<span><p>Ethical hacking is a form of legal hacking done with the permission of an organization to help increase its security. This operation also known as Penetration Testing ‚ÄúPentesting‚Äù. An ethical hacker has the skills, mindset, and tools of a hacker but is also trustworthy. As he performs these hacks as security tests for systems.</p>
</span>
